      <desc>Cyclistic 2023 Bike Share Analysis

This dashboard compares casual vs member riders to identify opportunities to increase membership.

Key Findings

1..Casual riders take longer trips on average compared to members.
2.Members show more consistent usage throughout the week.
3.Weekend demand is higher among casual riders.
4.Converting casual riders into members could increase long term customer value</desc>
